            <lg xml:id="TK212">
<l>tāḷāṟṟit tanta poruḷellān takkārkku</l>
<l>vēḷāṇmai ceytaṟ poruṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All the wealth acquired with perseverance by the worthy is for the exercise of benevolence.</l>
